data.description: Acreage!  Convenience!  Huge Garage!  So much potential for this one level home on 3.48 acres in a prime location.  Improvement projects started that need to be finished.  3rd bedroom in progress.  Great location for a home business or potential to rezone commercial... Or just enjoy the space and convenience!   Huge 24 x 50 Garage.  Fenced in area.  Chicken coup.  Just past the Knox county line.  Sold as is.
